---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
---

<LegalLayout
  title="About Us — Lingo7 Realty"
  description="Lingo7 Realty helps non-native English speakers pass the Florida real estate licensing exam — with parallel translation, audio, and spaced repetition built right into the material. Our mission: never let language stand between you and your license."
  canonicalUrl="https://lingo7realty.com/about/"
>
  <section class="about-hero">
    <img src="/favicon.svg" alt="" class="about-hero__icon" />
    <h1 class="about-hero__title">Our <span>mission</span></h1>
    <p class="about-hero__subtitle">To make sure language never stands between you and your real estate license.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="story">

    <div class="story__block">
      <span class="story__label">Where we came from</span>
      <h2>We grew out of <span>language learning</span></h2>
      <p>Lingo7 is a professional system for learning foreign languages. We turn unfamiliar text into something you actually understand: the translation is always one tap away, every word is read aloud in a natural human voice, and what you've learned comes back to you right before you'd forget it.</p>
      <p>For years we've helped people master a new language — so we know exactly how language gets in the way of capable, motivated people.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="story__block" style="margin-top: 56px;">
      <span class="story__label">The problem</span>
      <h2>Language shouldn't cost you a <span>career</span></h2>
      <p>On professional exams — and in real estate especially — people don't stumble over the subject, they stumble over the English. The textbook, the questions, the explanations: it's all in a second language, and your energy goes into decoding the words instead of mastering the material.</p>
      <p>We saw this happen again and again — and realized our experience in language learning could fix it.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="story__highlight">
      <p>So we moved into exam prep: we took everything we know about language and <span>built it straight into the exam material</span>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="story__block">
      <span class="story__label">The solution</span>
      <h2>Exam prep with <span>no language barrier</span></h2>
      <p>Lingo7 Realty is built so that anyone whose first language isn't English can study effectively and with confidence: every piece of material comes with parallel translation and audio in your native language, term flashcards and questions stick through spaced repetition, and adaptive tests take you to a passing score by the shortest path.</p>
      <p>The subject comes first. Language stops standing between you and your license.</p>
    </div>

  </section>
</LegalLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .about-hero {
    padding: 160px 40px 80px;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #fff 100%);
  }
  .about-hero__icon {
    width: 72px; height: 72px;
    margin: 0 auto 28px;
  }
  .about-hero__title {
    font-size: 52px; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .about-hero__title span { color: #34D399; }
  .about-hero__subtitle {
    font-size: 21px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Story */
  .story {
    padding: 80px 40px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .story__block {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }
  .story__block:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .story__label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #34D399;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .story__block h2 {
    font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .story__block h2 span { color: #34D399; }
  .story__block p {
    font-size: 18px; color: #444; line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .story__block p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* Highlight quote */
  .story__highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #ecfdf5 100%);
    border-left: 4px solid #34D399;
    border-radius: 0 16px 16px 0;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    margin: 40px 0;
  }
  .story__highlight p {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a2e;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .story__highlight span { color: #34D399; }

  /* Divider */
  .divider {
    width: 60px;
    height: 3px;
    background: #34D399;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero { padding: 110px 16px 60px; }
    .about-hero__icon { width: 56px; height: 56px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .about-hero__title { font-size: 34px; }
    .about-hero__subtitle { font-size: 17px; }
    .story { padding: 48px 16px; }
    .story__block h2 { font-size: 26px; }
    .story__block p { font-size: 16px; }
    .story__highlight { padding: 20px 20px; }
    .story__highlight p { font-size: 17px; }
  }
</style>
